Reputation of Excellence

When you enroll in our academic offerings, you gain a network of mentors and role models through our strong alumni community. We maintain alumni relationships through an online database, guest speakers, and professional networking.

Graduates from the Biology program at CSU Pueblo have achieved success in many careers and sectors, and many have continued their studies in graduate programs. Below are some of our graduates which includes their career paths.

If you are a CSU Pueblo Department of Biology graduate and have news you would like to share, please contact our department today!
